>					<br/>Lost or Damaged Packages<br/>We are not responsible for items lost in transit. If your package arrives damaged, please contact us within 7 days of delivery at emails@longmouth.world with your order number and photos of the item.<br/>					<br/>Refunds<br/>Refunds are issued only for eligible returned items. Shipping fees are non-refundable.<br/>					<br/>Return Form<br/>While we do not provide prepaid return labels, we recommend including your order number inside the package to help us process your return efficiently. </div></div></div></div><div data-w-tab="Tab 3" class="w-tab-pane w--tab-active"><div class="boring__page"><div class="boring__stuff"><h1 class="boring__heading">terms of service</h1><div class="boring__text">Effective Date: June 18, 2025 Company: Long Mouth Collectibles ApS Website: www.longmouth.world				<br/><br/>1. Overview<br/>By using www.longmouth.world (the &quot;Site&quot;), operated by Long Mouth Collectibles ApS (&quot;we&quot;, &quot;us&quot;, or &quot;our&quot;), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. Please read them carefully before using our Site or purchasing any products.				<br/><br/>2. Eligibility<br/>You must be at least 18 years old to use this Site or place an order. By using the Site, you confirm that you are legally able to form a binding contract in your jurisdiction.				<br/><br/>3. Orders &amp; Payment<br/>We accept the following payment methods: - Credit Cards<br/> - PayPal<br/> - MobilePay (only in Denmark)			<br/>All prices are listed in EUR or USD and include applicable VAT where required. You are responsible for any additional customs duties or import taxes based on your shipping location.		<br/><br/>4. Shipping<br/>We ship globally from both the EU and the US.<br/>We do not currently ship to: Cuba, Iran, Indonesia, North Korea, Syria, Ukraine, Russia, Venezuela, or Belarus. Shipping times and fees vary by region and will be displayed at checkout.		<br/><br/>5. Returns &amp; Cancellations<br/>You may